**Table:** `scan_history`

| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | INTEGER | Primary key (auto-increment) |
| timestamp | DATETIME | When the scan was performed |
| network_cidr | VARCHAR(50) | Network scanned (e.g., "192.168.1.0/24") |
| online_hosts | TEXT | JSON array of discovered hosts |
| total_hosts | INTEGER | Count of online hosts found |

**Example Record:**
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "timestamp": "2026-02-12 17:15:30",
  "network_cidr": "192.168.1.0/24",
  "online_hosts": "[{\"ip\":\"192.168.1.1\",\"hostname\":\"router.local\",\"status\":\"online\"}]",
  "total_hosts": 1
}
